            "**cancelAtPeriodEnd**: The cancellation period end flag.",
            "**collectionMethod**: The description of payment collection method.",
            "**created**: The creation timestamp.",
            "**currentPeriodEnd**: The end of period timestamp.",
            "**currentPeriodStart**: The start of period timestamp.",
            "**plan**: The plan used during subsribing.",
            "**status**: The status of subscription."
